## Notice on third-party content

This repository contains references to:
- Official NUEDC (National Undergraduate Electronic Design Contest) problem PDFs
  located in `赛题/`. These remain the property of their respective copyright
  holders and are included only for personal study and contest preparation.
  If you redistribute this repository, please verify the licensing status of
  these PDFs in your jurisdiction.
- Datasheets and reference designs from STMicroelectronics, Texas Instruments,
  Vishay, Infineon and others are referenced only by URL — no datasheet PDFs
  are bundled in this repository.
- Component photos / screenshots originate from the contributors and may be
  reused under the terms above.

Code samples, schematic descriptions, BOM lists and Markdown tutorials in
`备赛系统/` are original content and fall under the MIT license above.
